IF EXISTS
    (SELECT *
     FROM [sys].[objects] o
     WHERE [o].[type] = 'U'
     AND [o].[is_ms_shipped] = 0
     AND NOT EXISTS (SELECT *
         FROM [sys].[extended_properties] AS [ep]
         WHERE [ep].[major_id] = [o].[object_id]
             AND [ep].[minor_id] = 0
             AND [ep].[class] = 1
             AND [ep].[name] = N'microsoft_database_tools_support'
    )
)
SELECT 1 ELSE SELECT 0

IF EXISTS
    (SELECT *
     FROM [sys].[objects] o
     WHERE [o].[type] = 'U'
     AND [o].[is_ms_shipped] = 0
     AND NOT EXISTS (SELECT *
         FROM [sys].[extended_properties] AS [ep]
         WHERE [ep].[major_id] = [o].[object_id]
             AND [ep].[minor_id] = 0
             AND [ep].[class] = 1
             AND [ep].[name] = N'microsoft_database_tools_support'
    )
)
SELECT 1 ELSE SELECT 0

SELECT [t].[Id], [t].[Amount], [t].[CompanyId], [t].[Date], [t].[Description], [t].[Number], [t].[Type], [t0].[Id], [t0].[CompanyId], [t0].[DocsId], [t0].[Amount], [t0].[DishId], [t0].[Number], [t0].[Price], [t0].[Quantity], [t0].[Id0], [t0].[CategoriesId], [t0].[Code], [t0].[CompanyId0], [t0].[Description], [t0].[KKal], [t0].[Name], [t0].[PictureId], [t0].[Price0], [t0].[ReadyWeight]
FROM (
    SELECT TOP(2) [d].[Id], [d].[Amount], [d].[CompanyId], [d].[Date], [d].[Description], [d].[Number], [d].[Type]
    FROM [Docs] AS [d]
    WHERE (([d].[Id] = @__id_0) AND @__id_0 IS NOT NULL) AND (([d].[CompanyId] = @__GetCompanyID_1) AND @__GetCompanyID_1 IS NOT NULL)
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [d0].[Id], [d0].[CompanyId], [d0].[DocsId], [d0].[Amount], [d0].[DishId], [d0].[Number], [d0].[Price], [d0].[Quantity], [d1].[Id] AS [Id0], [d1].[CategoriesId], [d1].[Code], [d1].[CompanyId] AS [CompanyId0], [d1].[Description], [d1].[KKal], [d1].[Name], [d1].[PictureId], [d1].[Price] AS [Price0], [d1].[ReadyWeight]
    FROM [DocLines] AS [d0]
    INNER JOIN [Dishes] AS [d1] ON [d0].[DishId] = [d1].[Id]
) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[DocsId]
ORDER BY [t].[Id], [t0].[Id], [t0].[CompanyId], [t0].[DocsId], [t0].[Id0]

IF EXISTS
    (SELECT *
     FROM [sys].[objects] o
     WHERE [o].[type] = 'U'
     AND [o].[is_ms_shipped] = 0
     AND NOT EXISTS (SELECT *
         FROM [sys].[extended_properties] AS [ep]
         WHERE [ep].[major_id] = [o].[object_id]
             AND [ep].[minor_id] = 0
             AND [ep].[class] = 1
             AND [ep].[name] = N'microsoft_database_tools_support'
    )
)
SELECT 1 ELSE SELECT 0

    (SELECT *
     FROM [sys].[objects] o
     WHERE [o].[type] = 'U'
     AND [o].[is_ms_shipped] = 0
     AND NOT EXISTS (SELECT *
         FROM [sys].[extended_properties] AS [ep]
         WHERE [ep].[major_id] = [o].[object_id]
             AND [ep].[minor_id] = 0
             AND [ep].[class] = 1
             AND [ep].[name] = N'microsoft_database_tools_support'
    )
)
SELECT 1 ELSE SELECT 0

    (SELECT *
     FROM [sys].[objects] o
     WHERE [o].[type] = 'U'
     AND [o].[is_ms_shipped] = 0
     AND NOT EXISTS (SELECT *
         FROM [sys].[extended_properties] AS [ep]
         WHERE [ep].[major_id] = [o].[object_id]
             AND [ep].[minor_id] = 0
             AND [ep].[class] = 1
             AND [ep].[name] = N'microsoft_database_tools_support'
    )
)
SELECT 1 ELSE SELECT 0

SELECT [t].[Id], [t].[Amount], [t].[CompanyId], [t].[Date], [t].[Description], [t].[Number], [t].[Type], [t0].[Id], [t0].[CompanyId], [t0].[DocsId], [t0].[Amount], [t0].[DishId], [t0].[Number], [t0].[Price], [t0].[Quantity], [t0].[Id0], [t0].[CategoriesId], [t0].[Code], [t0].[CompanyId0], [t0].[Description], [t0].[KKal], [t0].[Name], [t0].[PictureId], [t0].[Price0], [t0].[ReadyWeight]
FROM (
    SELECT TOP(2) [d].[Id], [d].[Amount], [d].[CompanyId], [d].[Date], [d].[Description], [d].[Number], [d].[Type]
    FROM [Docs] AS [d]
    WHERE (([d].[Id] = @__id_0) AND @__id_0 IS NOT NULL) AND (([d].[CompanyId] = @__GetCompanyID_1) AND @__GetCompanyID_1 IS NOT NULL)
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [d0].[Id], [d0].[CompanyId], [d0].[DocsId], [d0].[Amount], [d0].[DishId], [d0].[Number], [d0].[Price], [d0].[Quantity], [d1].[Id] AS [Id0], [d1].[CategoriesId], [d1].[Code], [d1].[CompanyId] AS [CompanyId0], [d1].[Description], [d1].[KKal], [d1].[Name], [d1].[PictureId], [d1].[Price] AS [Price0], [d1].[ReadyWeight]
    FROM [DocLines] AS [d0]
    INNER JOIN [Dishes] AS [d1] ON [d0].[DishId] = [d1].[Id]
) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[DocsId]
ORDER BY [t].[Id], [t0].[Id], [t0].[CompanyId], [t0].[DocsId], [t0].[Id0]

SELECT [t].[Id], [t].[Amount], [t].[CompanyId], [t].[Date], [t].[Description], [t].[Number], [t].[Type], [t0].[Id], [t0].[CompanyId], [t0].[DocsId], [t0].[Amount], [t0].[DishId], [t0].[Number], [t0].[Price], [t0].[Quantity], [t0].[Id0], [t0].[CategoriesId], [t0].[Code], [t0].[CompanyId0], [t0].[Description], [t0].[KKal], [t0].[Name], [t0].[PictureId], [t0].[Price0], [t0].[ReadyWeight]
FROM (
    SELECT TOP(2) [d].[Id], [d].[Amount], [d].[CompanyId], [d].[Date], [d].[Description], [d].[Number], [d].[Type]
    FROM [Docs] AS [d]
    WHERE (([d].[Id] = @__id_0) AND @__id_0 IS NOT NULL) AND (([d].[CompanyId] = @__GetCompanyID_1) AND @__GetCompanyID_1 IS NOT NULL)
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [d0].[Id], [d0].[CompanyId], [d0].[DocsId], [d0].[Amount], [d0].[DishId], [d0].[Number], [d0].[Price], [d0].[Quantity], [d1].[Id] AS [Id0], [d1].[CategoriesId], [d1].[Code], [d1].[CompanyId] AS [CompanyId0], [d1].[Description], [d1].[KKal], [d1].[Name], [d1].[PictureId], [d1].[Price] AS [Price0], [d1].[ReadyWeight]
    FROM [DocLines] AS [d0]
    INNER JOIN [Dishes] AS [d1] ON [d0].[DishId] = [d1].[Id]
) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[DocsId]

    (SELECT *
     FROM [sys].[objects] o
     WHERE [o].[type] = 'U'
     AND [o].[is_ms_shipped] = 0
     AND NOT EXISTS (SELECT *
         FROM [sys].[extended_properties] AS [ep]
         WHERE [ep].[major_id] = [o].[object_id]
             AND [ep].[minor_id] = 0
             AND [ep].[class] = 1
             AND [ep].[name] = N'microsoft_database_tools_support'
    )
)

    SELECT TOP(2) [d].[Id], [d].[Amount], [d].[CompanyId], [d].[Date], [d].[Description], [d].[Number], [d].[Type]

    WHERE (([d].[Id] = @__id_0) AND @__id_0 IS NOT NULL) AND (([d].[CompanyId] = @__GetCompanyID_1) AND @__GetCompanyID_1 IS NOT NULL)

2019-10-28 10:56:48.347 +02:00 [Information] Microsoft.EntityFrameworkCore.Database.Command: Executing DbCommand [Parameters=[], CommandType='Text', CommandTimeout='30']

IF EXISTS
    (SELECT *
     FROM [sys].[objects] o
     WHERE [o].[type] = 'U'
     AND [o].[is_ms_shipped] = 0
     AND NOT EXISTS (SELECT *
         FROM [sys].[extended_properties] AS [ep]
         WHERE [ep].[major_id] = [o].[object_id]
             AND [ep].[minor_id] = 0
             AND [ep].[class] = 1

LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [d0].[Id], [d0].[CompanyId], [d0].[DocsId], [d0].[Amount], [d0].[DishId], [d0].[Number], [d0].[Price], [d0].[Quantity], [d1].[Id] AS [Id0], [d1].[CategoriesId], [d1].[Code], [d1].[CompanyId] AS [CompanyId0], [d1].[Description], [d1].[KKal], [d1].[Name], [d1].[PictureId], [d1].[Price] AS [Price0], [d1].[ReadyWeight]
    FROM [DocLines] AS [d0]
    INNER JOIN [Dishes] AS [d1] ON [d0].[DishId] = [d1].[Id]
) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[DocsId]
ORDER BY [t].[Id], [t0].[Id], [t0].[CompanyId], [t0].[DocsId], [t0].[Id0]

    (SELECT *
     FROM [sys].[objects] o
     WHERE [o].[type] = 'U'
     AND [o].[is_ms_shipped] = 0
     AND NOT EXISTS (SELECT *
         FROM [sys].[extended_properties] AS [ep]
         WHERE [ep].[major_id] = [o].[object_id]
             AND [ep].[minor_id] = 0
             AND [ep].[class] = 1
             AND [ep].[name] = N'microsoft_database_tools_support'
    )
)
SELECT 1 ELSE SELECT 0

SELECT [t].[Id], [t].[Amount], [t].[CompanyId], [t].[Date], [t].[Description], [t].[Number], [t].[Type], [t0].[Id], [t0].[CompanyId], [t0].[DocsId], [t0].[Amount], [t0].[DishId], [t0].[Number], [t0].[Price], [t0].[Quantity], [t0].[Id0], [t0].[CategoriesId], [t0].[Code], [t0].[CompanyId0], [t0].[Description], [t0].[KKal], [t0].[Name], [t0].[PictureId], [t0].[Price0], [t0].[ReadyWeight]
FROM (
    SELECT TOP(2) [d].[Id], [d].[Amount], [d].[CompanyId], [d].[Date], [d].[Description], [d].[Number], [d].[Type]
    FROM [Docs] AS [d]
    WHERE (([d].[Id] = @__id_0) AND @__id_0 IS NOT NULL) AND (([d].[CompanyId] = @__GetCompanyID_1) AND @__GetCompanyID_1 IS NOT NULL)
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [d0].[Id], [d0].[CompanyId], [d0].[DocsId], [d0].[Amount], [d0].[DishId], [d0].[Number], [d0].[Price], [d0].[Quantity], [d1].[Id] AS [Id0], [d1].[CategoriesId], [d1].[Code], [d1].[CompanyId] AS [CompanyId0], [d1].[Description], [d1].[KKal], [d1].[Name], [d1].[PictureId], [d1].[Price] AS [Price0], [d1].[ReadyWeight]
    FROM [DocLines] AS [d0]
    INNER JOIN [Dishes] AS [d1] ON [d0].[DishId] = [d1].[Id]
) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[DocsId]

SELECT [t].[Id], [t].[Amount], [t].[CompanyId], [t].[Date], [t].[Description], [t].[Number], [t].[Type], [t0].[Id], [t0].[CompanyId], [t0].[DocsId], [t0].[Amount], [t0].[DishId], [t0].[Number], [t0].[Price], [t0].[Quantity], [t0].[Id0], [t0].[CategoriesId], [t0].[Code], [t0].[CompanyId0], [t0].[Description], [t0].[KKal], [t0].[Name], [t0].[PictureId], [t0].[Price0], [t0].[ReadyWeight]
FROM (
    SELECT TOP(2) [d].[Id], [d].[Amount], [d].[CompanyId], [d].[Date], [d].[Description], [d].[Number], [d].[Type]
    FROM [Docs] AS [d]
    WHERE (([d].[Id] = @__id_0) AND @__id_0 IS NOT NULL) AND (([d].[CompanyId] = @__GetCompanyID_1) AND @__GetCompanyID_1 IS NOT NULL)
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [d0].[Id], [d0].[CompanyId], [d0].[DocsId], [d0].[Amount], [d0].[DishId], [d0].[Number], [d0].[Price], [d0].[Quantity], [d1].[Id] AS [Id0], [d1].[CategoriesId], [d1].[Code], [d1].[CompanyId] AS [CompanyId0], [d1].[Description], [d1].[KKal], [d1].[Name], [d1].[PictureId], [d1].[Price] AS [Price0], [d1].[ReadyWeight]
    FROM [DocLines] AS [d0]
    INNER JOIN [Dishes] AS [d1] ON [d0].[DishId] = [d1].[Id]
) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[DocsId]
ORDER BY [t].[Id], [t0].[Id], [t0].[CompanyId], [t0].[DocsId], [t0].[Id0]

FROM (
    SELECT TOP(2) [d].[Id], [d].[Amount], [d].[CompanyId], [d].[Date], [d].[Description], [d].[Number], [d].[Type]
    FROM [Docs] AS [d]
    WHERE (([d].[Id] = @__id_0) AND @__id_0 IS NOT NULL) AND (([d].[CompanyId] = @__GetCompanyID_1) AND @__GetCompanyID_1 IS NOT NULL)
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [d0].[Id], [d0].[CompanyId], [d0].[DocsId], [d0].[Amount], [d0].[DishId], [d0].[Number], [d0].[Price], [d0].[Quantity], [d1].[Id] AS [Id0], [d1].[CategoriesId], [d1].[Code], [d1].[CompanyId] AS [CompanyId0], [d1].[Description], [d1].[KKal], [d1].[Name], [d1].[PictureId], [d1].[Price] AS [Price0], [d1].[ReadyWeight]
    FROM [DocLines] AS [d0]
    INNER JOIN [Dishes] AS [d1] ON [d0].[DishId] = [d1].[Id]
) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[DocsId]

    SELECT TOP(2) [d].[Id], [d].[Amount], [d].[CompanyId], [d].[Date], [d].[Description], [d].[Number], [d].[Type]
    FROM [Docs] AS [d]
    WHERE (([d].[Id] = @__id_0) AND @__id_0 IS NOT NULL) AND (([d].[CompanyId] = @__GetCompanyID_1) AND @__GetCompanyID_1 IS NOT NULL)
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [d0].[Id], [d0].[CompanyId], [d0].[DocsId], [d0].[Amount], [d0].[DishId], [d0].[Number], [d0].[Price], [d0].[Quantity], [d1].[Id] AS [Id0], [d1].[CategoriesId], [d1].[Code], [d1].[CompanyId] AS [CompanyId0], [d1].[Description], [d1].[KKal], [d1].[Name], [d1].[PictureId], [d1].[Price] AS [Price0], [d1].[ReadyWeight]
    FROM [DocLines] AS [d0]
    INNER JOIN [Dishes] AS [d1] ON [d0].[DishId] = [d1].[Id]
) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[DocsId]

SELECT [t].[Id], [t].[Amount], [t].[CompanyId], [t].[Date], [t].[Description], [t].[Number], [t].[Type], [t0].[Id], [t0].[CompanyId], [t0].[DocsId], [t0].[Amount], [t0].[DishId], [t0].[Number], [t0].[Price], [t0].[Quantity], [t0].[Id0], [t0].[CategoriesId], [t0].[Code], [t0].[CompanyId0], [t0].[Description], [t0].[KKal], [t0].[Name], [t0].[PictureId], [t0].[Price0], [t0].[ReadyWeight]
FROM (
    SELECT TOP(2) [d].[Id], [d].[Amount], [d].[CompanyId], [d].[Date], [d].[Description], [d].[Number], [d].[Type]
    FROM [Docs] AS [d]
    WHERE (([d].[Id] = @__id_0) AND @__id_0 IS NOT NULL) AND (([d].[CompanyId] = @__GetCompanyID_1) AND @__GetCompanyID_1 IS NOT NULL)
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [d0].[Id], [d0].[CompanyId], [d0].[DocsId], [d0].[Amount], [d0].[DishId], [d0].[Number], [d0].[Price], [d0].[Quantity], [d1].[Id] AS [Id0], [d1].[CategoriesId], [d1].[Code], [d1].[CompanyId] AS [CompanyId0], [d1].[Description], [d1].[KKal], [d1].[Name], [d1].[PictureId], [d1].[Price] AS [Price0], [d1].[ReadyWeight]
    FROM [DocLines] AS [d0]
    INNER JOIN [Dishes] AS [d1] ON [d0].[DishId] = [d1].[Id]
) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[DocsId]
ORDER BY [t].[Id], [t0].[Id], [t0].[CompanyId], [t0].[DocsId], [t0].[Id0]

     FROM [sys].[objects] o

    SELECT TOP(2) [d].[Id], [d].[Amount], [d].[CompanyId], [d].[Date], [d].[Description], [d].[Number], [d].[Type]
    FROM [Docs] AS [d]
    WHERE (([d].[Id] = @__id_0) AND @__id_0 IS NOT NULL) AND (([d].[CompanyId] = @__GetCompanyID_1) AND @__GetCompanyID_1 IS NOT NULL)
) AS [t]

) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[DocsId]

SELECT [t].[Id], [t].[Amount], [t].[CompanyId], [t].[Date], [t].[Description], [t].[Number], [t].[Type], [t0].[Id], [t0].[CompanyId], [t0].[DocsId], [t0].[Amount], [t0].[DishId], [t0].[Number], [t0].[Price], [t0].[Quantity], [t0].[Id0], [t0].[CategoriesId], [t0].[Code], [t0].[CompanyId0], [t0].[Description], [t0].[KKal], [t0].[Name], [t0].[PictureId], [t0].[Price0], [t0].[ReadyWeight]
FROM (
    SELECT TOP(2) [d].[Id], [d].[Amount], [d].[CompanyId], [d].[Date], [d].[Description], [d].[Number], [d].[Type]
    FROM [Docs] AS [d]
    WHERE (([d].[Id] = @__id_0) AND @__id_0 IS NOT NULL) AND (([d].[CompanyId] = @__GetCompanyID_1) AND @__GetCompanyID_1 IS NOT NULL)
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [d0].[Id], [d0].[CompanyId], [d0].[DocsId], [d0].[Amount], [d0].[DishId], [d0].[Number], [d0].[Price], [d0].[Quantity], [d1].[Id] AS [Id0], [d1].[CategoriesId], [d1].[Code], [d1].[CompanyId] AS [CompanyId0], [d1].[Description], [d1].[KKal], [d1].[Name], [d1].[PictureId], [d1].[Price] AS [Price0], [d1].[ReadyWeight]
    FROM [DocLines] AS [d0]

) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[DocsId]
ORDER BY [t].[Id], [t0].[Id], [t0].[CompanyId], [t0].[DocsId], [t0].[Id0]

     FROM [sys].[objects] o
     WHERE [o].[type] = 'U'
     AND [o].[is_ms_shipped] = 0
     AND NOT EXISTS (SELECT *
         FROM [sys].[extended_properties] AS [ep]

)

SELECT [t].[Id], [t].[Amount], [t].[CompanyId], [t].[Date], [t].[Description], [t].[Number], [t].[Type], [t0].[Id], [t0].[CompanyId], [t0].[DocsId], [t0].[Amount], [t0].[DishId], [t0].[Number], [t0].[Price], [t0].[Quantity], [t0].[Id0], [t0].[CategoriesId], [t0].[Code], [t0].[CompanyId0], [t0].[Description], [t0].[KKal], [t0].[Name], [t0].[PictureId], [t0].[Price0], [t0].[ReadyWeight]
FROM (
    SELECT TOP(2) [d].[Id], [d].[Amount], [d].[CompanyId], [d].[Date], [d].[Description], [d].[Number], [d].[Type]
    FROM [Docs] AS [d]
    WHERE (([d].[Id] = @__id_0) AND @__id_0 IS NOT NULL) AND (([d].[CompanyId] = @__GetCompanyID_1) AND @__GetCompanyID_1 IS NOT NULL)
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [d0].[Id], [d0].[CompanyId], [d0].[DocsId], [d0].[Amount], [d0].[DishId], [d0].[Number], [d0].[Price], [d0].[Quantity], [d1].[Id] AS [Id0], [d1].[CategoriesId], [d1].[Code], [d1].[CompanyId] AS [CompanyId0], [d1].[Description], [d1].[KKal], [d1].[Name], [d1].[PictureId], [d1].[Price] AS [Price0], [d1].[ReadyWeight]
    FROM [DocLines] AS [d0]
    INNER JOIN [Dishes] AS [d1] ON [d0].[DishId] = [d1].[Id]
) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[DocsId]
ORDER BY [t].[Id], [t0].[Id], [t0].[CompanyId], [t0].[DocsId], [t0].[Id0]

SELECT [t].[Id], [t].[Amount], [t].[CompanyId], [t].[Date], [t].[Description], [t].[Number], [t].[Type], [t0].[Id], [t0].[Amount], [t0].[CompanyId], [t0].[DishId], [t0].[DocsId], [t0].[Number], [t0].[Price], [t0].[Quantity], [t0].[Id0], [t0].[CategoriesId], [t0].[Code], [t0].[CompanyId0], [t0].[Description], [t0].[KKal], [t0].[Name], [t0].[PictureId], [t0].[Price0], [t0].[ReadyWeight]
FROM (
    SELECT TOP(2) [d].[Id], [d].[Amount], [d].[CompanyId], [d].[Date], [d].[Description], [d].[Number], [d].[Type]
    FROM [Docs] AS [d]
    WHERE (([d].[Id] = @__id_0) AND @__id_0 IS NOT NULL) AND (([d].[CompanyId] = @__GetCompanyID_1) AND @__GetCompanyID_1 IS NOT NULL)
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [d0].[Id], [d0].[Amount], [d0].[CompanyId], [d0].[DishId], [d0].[DocsId], [d0].[Number], [d0].[Price], [d0].[Quantity], [d1].[Id] AS [Id0], [d1].[CategoriesId], [d1].[Code], [d1].[CompanyId] AS [CompanyId0], [d1].[Description], [d1].[KKal], [d1].[Name], [d1].[PictureId], [d1].[Price] AS [Price0], [d1].[ReadyWeight]
    FROM [DocLines] AS [d0]
    INNER JOIN [Dishes] AS [d1] ON [d0].[DishId] = [d1].[Id]
) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[DocsId]
ORDER BY [t].[Id], [t0].[Id], [t0].[Id0]

SELECT [t].[Id], [t].[Amount], [t].[CompanyId], [t].[Date], [t].[Description], [t].[Number], [t].[Type], [t0].[Id], [t0].[Amount], [t0].[CompanyId], [t0].[DishId], [t0].[DocsId], [t0].[Number], [t0].[Price], [t0].[Quantity], [t0].[Id0], [t0].[CategoriesId], [t0].[Code], [t0].[CompanyId0], [t0].[Description], [t0].[KKal], [t0].[Name], [t0].[PictureId], [t0].[Price0], [t0].[ReadyWeight]

    SELECT TOP(2) [d].[Id], [d].[Amount], [d].[CompanyId], [d].[Date], [d].[Description], [d].[Number], [d].[Type]
    FROM [Docs] AS [d]
    WHERE (([d].[Id] = @__id_0) AND @__id_0 IS NOT NULL) AND (([d].[CompanyId] = @__GetCompanyID_1) AND @__GetCompanyID_1 IS NOT NULL)
) AS [t]

) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[DocsId]

SELECT [t].[Id], [t].[Amount], [t].[CompanyId], [t].[Date], [t].[Description], [t].[Number], [t].[Type], [t0].[Id], [t0].[Amount], [t0].[CompanyId], [t0].[DishId], [t0].[DocsId], [t0].[Number], [t0].[Price], [t0].[Quantity], [t0].[Id0], [t0].[CategoriesId], [t0].[Code], [t0].[CompanyId0], [t0].[Description], [t0].[KKal], [t0].[Name], [t0].[PictureId], [t0].[Price0], [t0].[ReadyWeight]
FROM (
    SELECT TOP(2) [d].[Id], [d].[Amount], [d].[CompanyId], [d].[Date], [d].[Description], [d].[Number], [d].[Type]
    FROM [Docs] AS [d]
    WHERE (([d].[Id] = @__id_0) AND @__id_0 IS NOT NULL) AND (([d].[CompanyId] = @__GetCompanyID_1) AND @__GetCompanyID_1 IS NOT NULL)
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [d0].[Id], [d0].[Amount], [d0].[CompanyId], [d0].[DishId], [d0].[DocsId], [d0].[Number], [d0].[Price], [d0].[Quantity], [d1].[Id] AS [Id0], [d1].[CategoriesId], [d1].[Code], [d1].[CompanyId] AS [CompanyId0], [d1].[Description], [d1].[KKal], [d1].[Name], [d1].[PictureId], [d1].[Price] AS [Price0], [d1].[ReadyWeight]
    FROM [DocLines] AS [d0]
    INNER JOIN [Dishes] AS [d1] ON [d0].[DishId] = [d1].[Id]
) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[DocsId]
ORDER BY [t].[Id], [t0].[Id], [t0].[Id0]

    FROM [Docs] AS [d]
    WHERE (([d].[Id] = @__id_0) AND @__id_0 IS NOT NULL) AND (([d].[CompanyId] = @__GetCompanyID_1) AND @__GetCompanyID_1 IS NOT NULL)
) AS [t]

    INNER JOIN [Dishes] AS [d1] ON [d0].[DishId] = [d1].[Id]
) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[DocsId]

    (SELECT *
     FROM [sys].[objects] o
     WHERE [o].[type] = 'U'
     AND [o].[is_ms_shipped] = 0
     AND NOT EXISTS (SELECT *
         FROM [sys].[extended_properties] AS [ep]
         WHERE [ep].[major_id] = [o].[object_id]
             AND [ep].[minor_id] = 0
             AND [ep].[class] = 1
             AND [ep].[name] = N'microsoft_database_tools_support'
    )
)
SELECT 1 ELSE SELECT 0

    (SELECT *
     FROM [sys].[objects] o
     WHERE [o].[type] = 'U'
     AND [o].[is_ms_shipped] = 0
     AND NOT EXISTS (SELECT *
         FROM [sys].[extended_properties] AS [ep]
         WHERE [ep].[major_id] = [o].[object_id]
             AND [ep].[minor_id] = 0
             AND [ep].[class] = 1
             AND [ep].[name] = N'microsoft_database_tools_support'
    )
)
SELECT 1 ELSE SELECT 0

2019-10-28 13:57:25.919 +02:00 [Information] Microsoft.EntityFrameworkCore.Database.Command: Executing DbCommand [Parameters=[@__id_0='?' (DbType = Int32), @__GetCompanyID_1='?' (DbType = Int32)], CommandType='Text', CommandTimeout='30']
SELECT [t].[Id], [t].[Amount], [t].[CompanyId], [t].[Date], [t].[Description], [t].[Number], [t].[Type], [t0].[Id], [t0].[Amount], [t0].[CompanyId], [t0].[DocsId], [t0].[IngredientsId], [t0].[Number], [t0].[Price], [t0].[Quantity], [t0].[Id0], [t0].[CompanyId0], [t0].[MeasureUnit], [t0].[Name], [t0].[StockDate], [t0].[StockValue]
FROM (
    SELECT TOP(2) [d].[Id], [d].[Amount], [d].[CompanyId], [d].[Date], [d].[Description], [d].[Number], [d].[Type]
    FROM [Docs] AS [d]
    WHERE (([d].[Id] = @__id_0) AND @__id_0 IS NOT NULL) AND (([d].[CompanyId] = @__GetCompanyID_1) AND @__GetCompanyID_1 IS NOT NULL)
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [d0].[Id], [d0].[Amount], [d0].[CompanyId], [d0].[DocsId], [d0].[IngredientsId], [d0].[Number], [d0].[Price], [d0].[Quantity], [i].[Id] AS [Id0], [i].[CompanyId] AS [CompanyId0], [i].[MeasureUnit], [i].[Name], [i].[StockDate], [i].[StockValue]
    FROM [DocLines] AS [d0]
    INNER JOIN [Ingredients] AS [i] ON [d0].[IngredientsId] = [i].[Id]
) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[DocsId]
ORDER BY [t].[Id], [t0].[Id], [t0].[Id0]

FROM (
    SELECT TOP(2) [d].[Id], [d].[Amount], [d].[CompanyId], [d].[Date], [d].[Description], [d].[Number], [d].[Type]
    FROM [Docs] AS [d]
    WHERE (([d].[Id] = @__id_0) AND @__id_0 IS NOT NULL) AND (([d].[CompanyId] = @__GetCompanyID_1) AND @__GetCompanyID_1 IS NOT NULL)
) AS [t]

) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[DocsId]

) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [d0].[Id], [d0].[Amount], [d0].[CompanyId], [d0].[DocsId], [d0].[IngredientsId], [d0].[Number], [d0].[Price], [d0].[Quantity], [i].[Id] AS [Id0], [i].[CompanyId] AS [CompanyId0], [i].[MeasureUnit], [i].[Name], [i].[StockDate], [i].[StockValue]

    INNER JOIN [Ingredients] AS [i] ON [d0].[IngredientsId] = [i].[Id]
) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[DocsId]

) AS [t]

    (SELECT *
     FROM [sys].[objects] o
     WHERE [o].[type] = 'U'
     AND [o].[is_ms_shipped] = 0
     AND NOT EXISTS (SELECT *
         FROM [sys].[extended_properties] AS [ep]
         WHERE [ep].[major_id] = [o].[object_id]
             AND [ep].[minor_id] = 0
             AND [ep].[class] = 1
             AND [ep].[name] = N'microsoft_database_tools_support'
    )
)
SELECT 1 ELSE SELECT 0

SELECT [t].[Id], [t].[Amount], [t].[CompanyId], [t].[Date], [t].[Description], [t].[Number], [t].[Type], [t0].[Id], [t0].[Amount], [t0].[CompanyId], [t0].[DocsId], [t0].[IngredientsId], [t0].[Number], [t0].[Price], [t0].[Quantity], [t0].[Id0], [t0].[CompanyId0], [t0].[MeasureUnit], [t0].[Name], [t0].[StockDate], [t0].[StockValue]
FROM (
    SELECT TOP(2) [d].[Id], [d].[Amount], [d].[CompanyId], [d].[Date], [d].[Description], [d].[Number], [d].[Type]
    FROM [Docs] AS [d]
    WHERE (([d].[Id] = @__id_0) AND @__id_0 IS NOT NULL) AND (([d].[CompanyId] = @__GetCompanyID_1) AND @__GetCompanyID_1 IS NOT NULL)
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [d0].[Id], [d0].[Amount], [d0].[CompanyId], [d0].[DocsId], [d0].[IngredientsId], [d0].[Number], [d0].[Price], [d0].[Quantity], [i].[Id] AS [Id0], [i].[CompanyId] AS [CompanyId0], [i].[MeasureUnit], [i].[Name], [i].[StockDate], [i].[StockValue]
    FROM [DocLines] AS [d0]
    INNER JOIN [Ingredients] AS [i] ON [d0].[IngredientsId] = [i].[Id]
) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[DocsId]
ORDER BY [t].[Id], [t0].[Id], [t0].[Id0]

    (SELECT *
     FROM [sys].[objects] o
     WHERE [o].[type] = 'U'
     AND [o].[is_ms_shipped] = 0
     AND NOT EXISTS (SELECT *
         FROM [sys].[extended_properties] AS [ep]
         WHERE [ep].[major_id] = [o].[object_id]
             AND [ep].[minor_id] = 0
             AND [ep].[class] = 1
             AND [ep].[name] = N'microsoft_database_tools_support'
    )
)
SELECT 1 ELSE SELECT 0

SELECT [t].[Id], [t].[Amount], [t].[CompanyId], [t].[Date], [t].[Description], [t].[Number], [t].[Type], [t0].[Id], [t0].[Amount], [t0].[CompanyId], [t0].[DocsId], [t0].[IngredientsId], [t0].[Number], [t0].[Price], [t0].[Quantity], [t0].[Id0], [t0].[CompanyId0], [t0].[MeasureUnit], [t0].[Name], [t0].[StockDate], [t0].[StockValue]
FROM (
    SELECT TOP(2) [d].[Id], [d].[Amount], [d].[CompanyId], [d].[Date], [d].[Description], [d].[Number], [d].[Type]
    FROM [Docs] AS [d]
    WHERE (([d].[Id] = @__id_0) AND @__id_0 IS NOT NULL) AND (([d].[CompanyId] = @__GetCompanyID_1) AND @__GetCompanyID_1 IS NOT NULL)
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [d0].[Id], [d0].[Amount], [d0].[CompanyId], [d0].[DocsId], [d0].[IngredientsId], [d0].[Number], [d0].[Price], [d0].[Quantity], [i].[Id] AS [Id0], [i].[CompanyId] AS [CompanyId0], [i].[MeasureUnit], [i].[Name], [i].[StockDate], [i].[StockValue]

) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[DocsId]

    WHERE (([d].[Id] = @__id_0) AND @__id_0 IS NOT NULL) AND (([d].[CompanyId] = @__GetCompanyID_1) AND @__GetCompanyID_1 IS NOT NULL)
) AS [t]

FROM (
    SELECT TOP(2) [d].[Id], [d].[Amount], [d].[CompanyId], [d].[Date], [d].[Description], [d].[Number], [d].[Type]
    FROM [Docs] AS [d]
    WHERE (([d].[Id] = @__id_0) AND @__id_0 IS NOT NULL) AND (([d].[CompanyId] = @__GetCompanyID_1) AND @__GetCompanyID_1 IS NOT NULL)
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [d0].[Id], [d0].[Amount], [d0].[CompanyId], [d0].[DocsId], [d0].[IngredientsId], [d0].[Number], [d0].[Price], [d0].[Quantity], [i].[Id] AS [Id0], [i].[CompanyId] AS [CompanyId0], [i].[MeasureUnit], [i].[Name], [i].[StockDate], [i].[StockValue]

    SELECT TOP(2) [d].[Id], [d].[Amount], [d].[CompanyId], [d].[Date], [d].[Description], [d].[Number], [d].[Type]

    WHERE (([d].[Id] = @__id_0) AND @__id_0 IS NOT NULL) AND (([d].[CompanyId] = @__GetCompanyID_1) AND @__GetCompanyID_1 IS NOT NULL)
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (

FROM (
    SELECT TOP(2) [d].[Id], [d].[Amount], [d].[CompanyId], [d].[Date], [d].[Description], [d].[Number], [d].[Type]
    FROM [Docs] AS [d]
    WHERE (([d].[Id] = @__id_0) AND @__id_0 IS NOT NULL) AND (([d].[CompanyId] = @__GetCompanyID_1) AND @__GetCompanyID_1 IS NOT NULL)
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [d0].[Id], [d0].[Amount], [d0].[CompanyId], [d0].[DocsId], [d0].[IngredientsId], [d0].[Number], [d0].[Price], [d0].[Quantity], [i].[Id] AS [Id0], [i].[CompanyId] AS [CompanyId0], [i].[MeasureUnit], [i].[Name], [i].[StockDate], [i].[StockValue]
    FROM [DocLines] AS [d0]
    INNER JOIN [Ingredients] AS [i] ON [d0].[IngredientsId] = [i].[Id]
) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[DocsId]
ORDER BY [t].[Id], [t0].[Id], [t0].[Id0]

SELECT [t].[Id], [t].[Amount], [t].[CompanyId], [t].[Date], [t].[Description], [t].[Number], [t].[Type], [t0].[Id], [t0].[Amount], [t0].[CompanyId], [t0].[DocsId], [t0].[IngredientsId], [t0].[Number], [t0].[Price], [t0].[Quantity], [t0].[Id0], [t0].[CompanyId0], [t0].[MeasureUnit], [t0].[Name], [t0].[StockDate], [t0].[StockValue]
FROM (
    SELECT TOP(2) [d].[Id], [d].[Amount], [d].[CompanyId], [d].[Date], [d].[Description], [d].[Number], [d].[Type]
    FROM [Docs] AS [d]
    WHERE (([d].[Id] = @__id_0) AND @__id_0 IS NOT NULL) AND (([d].[CompanyId] = @__GetCompanyID_1) AND @__GetCompanyID_1 IS NOT NULL)
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [d0].[Id], [d0].[Amount], [d0].[CompanyId], [d0].[DocsId], [d0].[IngredientsId], [d0].[Number], [d0].[Price], [d0].[Quantity], [i].[Id] AS [Id0], [i].[CompanyId] AS [CompanyId0], [i].[MeasureUnit], [i].[Name], [i].[StockDate], [i].[StockValue]
    FROM [DocLines] AS [d0]
    INNER JOIN [Ingredients] AS [i] ON [d0].[IngredientsId] = [i].[Id]
) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[DocsId]
ORDER BY [t].[Id], [t0].[Id], [t0].[Id0]

2019-10-28 19:16:40.647 +02:00 [Information] Microsoft.EntityFrameworkCore.Database.Command: Executing DbCommand [Parameters=[], CommandType='Text', CommandTimeout='30']

IF EXISTS
    (SELECT *
     FROM [sys].[objects] o
     WHERE [o].[type] = 'U'
     AND [o].[is_ms_shipped] = 0
     AND NOT EXISTS (SELECT *
         FROM [sys].[extended_properties] AS [ep]
         WHERE [ep].[major_id] = [o].[object_id]
             AND [ep].[minor_id] = 0
             AND [ep].[class] = 1
             AND [ep].[name] = N'microsoft_database_tools_support'
    )
)
SELECT 1 ELSE SELECT 0

) AS [t]

    (SELECT *
     FROM [sys].[objects] o
     WHERE [o].[type] = 'U'
     AND [o].[is_ms_shipped] = 0
     AND NOT EXISTS (SELECT *
         FROM [sys].[extended_properties] AS [ep]

             AND [ep].[name] = N'microsoft_database_tools_support'
    )
)

SELECT [t].[Id], [t].[Amount], [t].[CompanyId], [t].[Date], [t].[Description], [t].[Number], [t].[Type], [t0].[Id], [t0].[Amount], [t0].[CompanyId], [t0].[DocsId], [t0].[IngredientsId], [t0].[Number], [t0].[Price], [t0].[Quantity], [t0].[Id0], [t0].[CompanyId0], [t0].[MeasureUnit], [t0].[Name], [t0].[StockDate], [t0].[StockValue]
FROM (
    SELECT TOP(2) [d].[Id], [d].[Amount], [d].[CompanyId], [d].[Date], [d].[Description], [d].[Number], [d].[Type]
    FROM [Docs] AS [d]
    WHERE (([d].[Id] = @__id_0) AND @__id_0 IS NOT NULL) AND (([d].[CompanyId] = @__GetCompanyID_1) AND @__GetCompanyID_1 IS NOT NULL)
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [d0].[Id], [d0].[Amount], [d0].[CompanyId], [d0].[DocsId], [d0].[IngredientsId], [d0].[Number], [d0].[Price], [d0].[Quantity], [i].[Id] AS [Id0], [i].[CompanyId] AS [CompanyId0], [i].[MeasureUnit], [i].[Name], [i].[StockDate], [i].[StockValue]
    FROM [DocLines] AS [d0]
    INNER JOIN [Ingredients] AS [i] ON [d0].[IngredientsId] = [i].[Id]
) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[DocsId]
ORDER BY [t].[Id], [t0].[Id], [t0].[Id0]
